# {{context|idiomatic|lang=en}} To cause a person to feel [[grief]] or [[sadness]].
#: ''He '''broke my heart''', so I broke his jaw.''
#* '''1976''', [[w:Elton John|Elton John]], ''[[w:Don't Go Breaking My Heart|Don't Go Breaking My Heart]]'',
#*: Don't go '''breaking my heart''' / ''I couldn't if I tried'' / Honey if I get restless / ''Baby you're not that kind.''
